'''PokéClicker''' is a clicker game originally made by '''Isha Dijcks (IshaD)''', based around the Kanto region. Around June 2017 [citation needed], IshaD, along with Aegyo, BaineGames, Qubit and dennism1997 started working on a complete rewrite of the project, with new regions and contents. Around 2018[citation needed], RedSparr0w joined the dev team.
The original version is playable on https://ishadijcks.github.io/, while the new (development) version is playable on https://pokeclicker-development.herokuapp.com/
